\f0\fs56 \cf2 Strawberry Rhubarb Crumble\
\pard\pardeftab720\li660\sl360\sa300\ql\qnatural

\i\fs40 \cf3 Feel free to experiment with the amount of sugar in this based on how sweet your berries are. For example, try it with 1/2 cup sugar tossed with the fruit, and make note - you might want it more/less sweet the next time around.
