1 tablespoon cornstarch
\f1 \uc0\u8232 
\f0 1/2 cup / 2 oz / 60 g natural cane sugar (or Muscovado sugar)\
1/2 lb. / 8 ounces / 225 g hulled medium strawberries, cut into quarters\
